{"tid":1472194,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【有圖 - 極不安】 805 荃灣刀手斬示威者 警黑勾結","createTime":"2019-08-14T13:23:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T04:38:39.000Z","uid":235711,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"cdc51ec4e40c8981a8b88f6f31f9c6136eedcb04","tid":1472194,"uid":235711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T13:23:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/soO3pp4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsoO3pp4.jpg&h=1e21337b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cu2vORK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCu2vORK.jpg&h=66da7228&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2019.8.14【1900】有已核實身分的醫護人員聯絡，提供兩張8月5日，荃灣被刀手斬示威者（圖）送院時傷勢的照片。<br />\n<br />\n該名醫護呼籲，希望市民認清什麼才是真正的暴力，又稱不會指責昨晚在機場集會動手的示威者，因為兩個月以來不少示威者都被警察或者黑社會攻擊致受傷，而傷勢之重，與昨日於機場被打的疑似公安及環時記者根本無從比較，「好多人已經為呢件事付出好多，現在唔係指責或者割席嘅時候」。<br />\n<br />\n以下為傷勢照片，或會引起嚴重不安，查看前請務必做好心理準備。<br />\n<br />\n左腳傷勢：<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/z0k1UL0.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz0k1UL0.jpg&d=ldtyJnQDYvl76HjiXEXVXM4e4tfxBia5339duguOAPM%3D&h=76b003b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/z0k1UL0.jpg</a><br />\n右手傷勢：<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/oeH3751.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoeH3751.jpg&d=ldtyJnQDYvl76HjiXEXVXM4e4tfxBia5339duguOAPM%3D&h=3e2045ad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/oeH3751.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JVYnEYw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJVYnEYw.png&h=b14507e3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b42fdcd2584ca36d0228e1aad22284e69005be6e","tid":1472194,"uid":171992,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T13:23:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/6yR8ycR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6yR8ycR.jpg&h=a587efad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141044_b70c4022f89dcf5617302fe3f20434af.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141044_b70c4022f89dcf5617302fe3f20434af.jpeg&h=b7bac505&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141056_6689ba9867dc55e5e3b796d75180758d.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141056_6689ba9867dc55e5e3b796d75180758d.jpeg&h=42f5c084&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141101_1e69ec3ac35774384c7044962c18e307.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141101_1e69ec3ac35774384c7044962c18e307.png&h=4a3dc024&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141106_a064336a869290c4a85c50e2c5342faf.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F14%2F141106_a064336a869290c4a85c50e2c5342faf.jpeg&h=42d70b2e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ab60f9b6d6ed742f91f1451dad4db5e1fb572a6a","tid":1472194,"uid":235711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T13:24:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b7ef4ca1cc53ae7d9f07ba4486a53a77c30f231d","tid":1472194,"uid":249979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T13:38:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z4kdK7K.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ4kdK7K.jpg&h=8672802c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kdv9iuk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fkdv9iuk.jpg&h=da06f494&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4972445a2b763db0edadfd3b2f579d452efcf58d","tid":1472194,"uid":84741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T13:46:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>警黑合作 破壞法治</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"c0862123a11d69f7718688ffe910acaa4d1e09df","tid":1472194,"uid":260367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T13:48:49.000Z","msg":"612 721 811"},{"pid":"b8a0dd9880c8c1b9fbfaa9e89e9551077d7008a0","tid":1472194,"uid":216789,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T13:52:36.000Z","msg":"<strong>慎防黑惡勢力蔓延禍港，提防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團</strong><br />\n<br />\n鑒於近日有無辜香港市民慘遭黑勢力人仕襲擊，現懇切呼籲各香港市民不論男女，請慎防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團，保障自身安全，萬事小心，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">切忌助長黑惡勢力氣焰</span></strong>"},{"pid":"20f11a99f629e3c2b6826acf718591709a663591","tid":1472194,"uid":248290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b7ef4ca1cc53ae7d9f07ba4486a53a77c30f231d","tid":1472194,"uid":249979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T13:38:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z4kdK7K.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ4kdK7K.jpg&h=8672802c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kdv9iuk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fkdv9iuk.jpg&h=da06f494&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T13:58:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fcd8c9da19ea9ff8aab76bc0ca272bc1d2aa019","tid":1472194,"uid":53577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T13:59:03.000Z","msg":"斬人嗰個分分鐘喺sdu黑警，你點知呀"},{"pid":"c658f5098a25a781f98fd4c2ea2fa3181ce446c3","tid":1472194,"uid":260325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T14:05:05.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"8